            <p>Add a commit hook to your Claude Code, Cursor, or Codex setup and Signal logs your session automatically every time you commit. Automatically capture the tools you used, the problems you solved, and how you got there. The more you work, the stronger your signal gets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

